OL,3,CWest Wickham KFC franchisee must pay
OL,4,Cworker nearly #70k
OL,6,FA KFC franchisee has been made to pay
OL,7,Fnearly #70,000 after a manager called
OL,8,Fan Indian worker a "slave" and forced
OL,9,Fhim to work extra hours, a tribunal
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FMadhesh Ravichandran from Tamil Nadu,
OL,13,Fbegan working at the West Wickham KFC
OL,14,Foutlet for Nexus Foods Limited in
OL,15,FJanuary 2023 and was soon working more
OL,16,Fhours than required in his contract,
OL,17,Fthe tribunal in London heard.
