OL,3,CWest Wickham KFC franchisee must pay
OL,4,Cworker nearly #70k
OL,6,FIn March 2023, Mr Ravichandran was
OL,7,Frefused annual leave and heard his
OL,8,Fboss Kajan Theiventhiram telling a
OL,9,Fcolleague he would prioritise Sri
OL,10,FLankan Tamil staff and referring to
OL,11,Fthe claimant as "this shit" and "this
OL,12,Fslave", the tribunal was told.
OL,14,FTribunal judge Paul Abbott found that
OL,15,FMr Ravichandran was "upset and
OL,16,Fhumiliated" and that the refusal of
OL,17,Fthe claimant's leave request was
OL,18,F"significantly influenced" by his race.
