OL,3,CWest Wickham KFC franchisee must pay
OL,4,Cworker nearly #70k
OL,6,FThe judge accepted the claimant's
OL,7,Fevidence that he was being "forced" to
OL,8,Fwork excessive hours because of Mr
OL,9,FTheiventhiram's "racially prejudiced
OL,10,Fattitude" towards him.
OL,12,FMonths later, Mr Ravichandran resigned
OL,13,Fbut no real investigation took place
OL,14,Finto his allegations, the tribunal
OL,15,Ffound.
OL,17,FJudge Abbott found that Mr
OL,18,FRavichandran was wrongfully dismissed
OL,19,Fand subjected to direct race
OL,20,Fdiscrimination, harassment related to
OL,21,Frace and victimisation.
